# Design

- Dark-first, high contrast, hairline borders, compact panels, keyboard-first.
- Tokenized styling only (`theme/tokens.zig`).
- Cursor/Vercel are inspiration only — no brand assets, logos, or trade dress.
- Agent surface: task cards, status labels, calm typography.
